      "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/28/1/285/4",
      "text": [
        ": قال رسول الله صلى الله عليه وآله: السخاء شجرة في الجنة أصلها و هي مظلة على الدنيا، من تعلق بغصن من اجتره إلى الجنة."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.basel-kadem": [
          "4.\tWith this chain of narrators, from Ahmad bin Abi Abdillah, from Ibn Faddal, from a man, from Hafs bin Ghiyath, from Abu Abdillah, peace be upon him, that he said: The Messenger of Allah, Allah’s blessings be upon him and his Family, said: Openhandedness is a tree whose root is in  Paradise and which shades upon this world. The one who adheres to a branch of it will be drawn to Paradise."
        ]
      }
